title: Price series for various commodities
description:
Description
Annual prices for eggs, chicken, copper, nails, oil and wheat.
Eggs, chicken, nails, oil and copper in $US; wheat in British pounds. All prices adjusted for inflation.
format: Makridakis, Wheelwright and Hyndman (1998) *Forecasting: methods and applications*, John Wiley & Sons: New York. Chapter 9.
